sources.description:
Drew Utley is tired of being pushed around at school. But when he and his band of outcast buddies run afoul of an evil genius, they find themselves in possession of a special suit that gives superpowers to whomever wears it. Now there's a new team of anti-bully vigilantes in town: P.U.N.K.S. This sci-fi adventure is sure to entertain the whole family!
